The paper deals with image segmentation using machine learning techniques, specifically for segmenting neuron membranes in 2D electron microscopy imagery. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also uses random forest classifiers and convolutional neural networks, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Additionally, the paper deals with the reconstruction of brain circuits, which falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with image processing techniques, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
